<lb n="0719b08" ed="T"/>他揭多馱都達<note n="0719013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麗＝囇【三】【甲】</note><note n="0719013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麗【大】，囇【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0719013"><lem wit="【大】">麗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">囇</rdg></app><note place="inline">六</note>達囉達囉<note place="inline">七</note>珊達<note n="0719014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【明】【甲】＊</note><note n="0719014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉【大】＊，羅【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0719014"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">羅</rdg></app>珊
